{"tid":392553,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［少圖］自制皮革鎖匙扣","createTime":"2017-09-08T14:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T09:09:48.000Z","uid":30696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1ca6742bf6abed86c64825cdeed46c456bc3bd3","tid":392553,"uid":30696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"講明先，呢個唔係教學，唔係for新手（雖然我係），純粹share下成個flow<br />\n唔接order，都冇能力咁做，新手問題儘答<br />\n所有設計圖都係自己畫嘅，用AutoCAD 1:1, 即係print出嚟就可以照住cut／打斬想要可以share，但最好就交換啦～唔洗畫到好靚，present到idea就得 （呢個post嘅原意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/whatsusername\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwhatsusername&d=7it%2F1bFr0qyUD3o5YqEL8ywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=c1629165\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/whatsusername</a><br />\nP.S. 基於3.38法斬畫嘅，啱用就拎去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nP.S.2 line weighting特別set到咁幼，為求準<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n設計圖：<br />\n藍色係斬位，黃色係削薄，其它應該就咁都睇得明<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/221136_82070bb651a2269957ffbd78e58a42c8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F221136_82070bb651a2269957ffbd78e58a42c8.png&h=c1cd293f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裁皮：<br />\n用日本新禧馬皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，底1.0, 面1.5<br />\n兩塊一齊（唔洗痴埋）磨下邊，咁之後打斬會準好多<br />\n用設計圖舖喺面皮輕輕印一印斬位，畫邊線，根據斬位印大力少少（修正設計圖走位問題）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/221357_ac0e8e84711245f0e221d92861f2fe16.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F221357_ac0e8e84711245f0e221d92861f2fe16.JPG&h=e76c490b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n削薄：<br />\n唔記得影相，我用斷削，面皮削到1.0, 底皮唔削<br />\n削薄冇咩好講，要練手感<br />\n痴埋一齊：<br />\n記得壓實接合位（<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊隻膠水痴皮好用？）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/221903_1b2e4766aeceae034882d8b3582c4a4e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F221903_1b2e4766aeceae034882d8b3582c4a4e.JPG&h=35ca08d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n打斬&amp;縫線：<br />\n用0.5白線，力度角度要一樣，線最影響件product靚唔靚<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/222257_a9e041f7f08eadc3b272491471c1f4cd.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F222257_a9e041f7f08eadc3b272491471c1f4cd.JPG&h=5f537cbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畫裝飾線&amp;削邊&amp;CMC磨邊：<br />\n裝飾線畫得唔夠好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/222536_1f85405779c10c18e1cd48ee1acb9138.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F222536_1f85405779c10c18e1cd48ee1acb9138.JPG&h=a1691b04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n封邊：<br />\n上多幾浸會滑啲～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/222809_0afcffc6cbafa3b040217ba9f958e380.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F222809_0afcffc6cbafa3b040217ba9f958e380.JPG&h=f20fe186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大功告成<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/222908_cd29fea263995588efed494252c5ff6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F222908_cd29fea263995588efed494252c5ff6d.jpg&h=801c1aa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/222908_55d0a9598215d0b61d296acb0aa32dd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F222908_55d0a9598215d0b61d296acb0aa32dd2.jpg&h=42b16be1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n下回預告<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/222938_d8a6cfbe78f3ee8308d90a1402ec75a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F222938_d8a6cfbe78f3ee8308d90a1402ec75a9.png&h=4ee3e3eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea9464fbb41369cb6a9d16c13127c750ff95173c","tid":392553,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:42:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a7d841fb2aec2b49620bc84804f36b0d3d2a6c1","tid":392553,"uid":30696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:44:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多匙咪唔得？</blockquote><br />\n正解，因為呢個淨係俾我用，會fit到漏，多匙要再改長少少<br />\n粒釘都要換個啱嘅size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083c48f213faa0f24064042f22a9c6df8c0ee7fa","tid":392553,"uid":30696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:45:21.000Z","msg":"btw唔好就咁用post嗰張設計圖，唔啱scale，想要問我拎A4嘅PDF，唔好曬紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aad427b6c81c2599b69c415d5a8fc783e41d2e8","tid":392553,"uid":5197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:45:53.000Z","msg":"睇完都唔識整"},{"pid":"db0f8e3646549624c39713c4ae03ba8dd8b93aab","tid":392553,"uid":30696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:47:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完都唔識整</blockquote><br />\n講咗唔係教學，我全部自學嘅，要摸幾次個flow先做得好，所以先share下睇有冇人啱用<br />\n邊度唔明都可以問嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd9831fa82fc0fe94d874083be4856efe805a4a","tid":392553,"uid":61676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T09:09:48.000Z","msg":"幾時有下回<br />\n學下野 交流下"}]}